plot: World renowned chef Gordon Ramsay puts aspiring young chefs through rigorous and devastating challenges at his restaurant in Hollywood, &"Hell's Kitchen&", to determine which of them will win the restaurant of their dreams. Their dreams are quickly becoming nightmares.   Written by
